# 🧠  Bilingualism CVAE: Contrastive learning and Variations in Bilingualism

## 🧪 Project Overview

This project investigates the variations in bilinguals by using CVAE, a contrastive learning methods

Key components:
- Collect and preprocess MRI data (fmriPrep)
- Train VAE and CVAE by using monolingual and bilinguals brains
- Get each brains VAE and CVAE vectors
- Map VAE and CVAE vectors to behavioral measures
- Synthetic twin brain, localize variations


